```plantuml
@startuml jquku_Matrix-Chatbot

actor User
participant "Matrix Homeserver" as MatrixServer
participant "Main Module" as Main
participant "Message Evaluation" as MessageEval
participant "NLP Module" as NLP
participant "Database Service" as DBService
participant "Response Management" as ResponseMgmt

User -> MatrixServer: Sends message
MatrixServer -> Main: Receives message event
Main -> MessageEval: Forwards message for evaluation
MessageEval -> NLP: Processes message text
NLP -> NLP: Lowercase, tokenize, lemmatize
NLP --> MessageEval: Returns processed text
MessageEval -> DBService: Queries knowledge base
DBService --> MessageEval: Returns matching knowledge
MessageEval -> ResponseMgmt: Passes evaluation results
ResponseMgmt -> DBService: Updates statistics
DBService --> ResponseMgmt: Confirms update
ResponseMgmt --> Main: Returns formatted response
Main -> MatrixServer: Sends response
MatrixServer -> User: Delivers response

@enduml
```